<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-white" data-controller="exercise-checker">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Exercise 4 -->
  <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-6 pb-8">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">4</span>
      Riscrivi le frasi sul quaderno sostituendo le congiunzioni con altre congiunzioni in modo che le frasi abbiano comunque senso. Osserva l'esempio.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="mb-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Elsa si è slogata una caviglia, <strong>quindi</strong> l'abbiamo portata dal dottore.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 pl-4">
          → <em>Elsa si è slogata una caviglia, <strong>perciò</strong> l'abbiamo portata dal dottore.</em>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <strong>Poiché</strong> sei arrivata prima, meriti un premio.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Umberto suona la chitarra <strong>e</strong> Rossella canta.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Il posto è libero, <strong>perciò</strong> puoi sederti.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Porto il pane, <strong>però</strong> non è fresco.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 5 -->
  <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">5</span>
      Completa con le congiunzioni adatte.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Chiudo la porta</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-28 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="perché" data-correct-answer="perché">
          <span class="text-gray-700">fa freddo.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Siamo molto amici</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-28 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="ma" data-correct-answer="ma">
          <span class="text-gray-700">non ci vediamo quasi mai</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-28 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="perché" data-correct-answer="perché">
          <span class="text-gray-700">abitiamo lontano.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">L'acqua è preziosa</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-28 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="perciò" data-correct-answer="perciò">
          <span class="text-gray-700">cerchiamo di non sprecarla.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Non so</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-28 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="se" data-correct-answer="se">
          <span class="text-gray-700">uscirò</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-28 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="o" data-correct-answer="o">
          <span class="text-gray-700">rimarrò in casa.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 6 -->
  <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="word-highlighter" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="true">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center flex-wrap gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">6</span>
      <span>Sottolinea congiunzioni coordinative<span class="inline-block w-5 h-5 bg-yellow-300 rounded ml-1 cursor-pointer" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="yellow" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span> e congiunzioni subordinative<span class="inline-block w-5 h-5 bg-purple-300 rounded ml-1 cursor-pointer" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="purple" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span>.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg cursor-pointer">
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> La squadra ha giocato bene <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">ma</span> ha perso.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Hai saputo <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="purple">che</span> Giuditta cambia scuola?</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Sono fratelli <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="purple">benché</span> non si assomiglino.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Andiamo a piedi <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">o</span> prendiamo le bici?</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Le mie competenze section -->
  <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-100 p-4 md:p-6 pb-8 rounded-lg">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-700 mb-6 text-center">
      Le mie competenze
    </h2>

    <!-- Exercise 7 -->
    <div data-controller="multiple-choice">
      <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg font-bold text-gray-700 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center">7</span>
        Leggi la seguente frase.
      </h3>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 mb-4">
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 font-semibold italic text-center">
          "Halyna va di rado in montagna, sebbene cammini volentieri."
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 font-semibold mb-3">Qual è l'unica affermazione vera?</p>

      <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg">
        <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-white rounded-lg px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50">
          <input type="checkbox" name="ex7" value="A" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
          <span class="text-gray-700">Nella frase ci sono soltanto una congiunzione e un avverbio.</span>
        </label>

        <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-white rounded-lg px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50">
          <input type="checkbox" name="ex7" value="B" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
          <span class="text-gray-700">Nella frase ci sono soltanto una locuzione avverbiale e una congiunzione.</span>
        </label>

        <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-white rounded-lg px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50">
          <input type="checkbox" name="ex7" value="C" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
          <span class="text-gray-700">Nella frase ci sono due avverbi e una congiunzione.</span>
        </label>

        <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-white rounded-lg px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50">
          <input type="checkbox" name="ex7" value="D" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
          <span class="text-gray-700">Nella frase ci sono una locuzione avverbiale, un avverbio e una congiunzione.</span>
        </label>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>

</div>
